{"tid":1235634,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"10月family trip，求福岡airbnb分享","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T03:01:44.000Z","uid":251949,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf299b17a20979c98e2366f8d36f5fbba4dd195","tid":1235634,"uid":251949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"10月一家五口去福岡自駕遊，<br />\n而家PLAN緊福岡＞由（湯）布院＞佐賀＞福岡。<br />\n今次帶阿爸阿媽，再加我一家三口（兩歲女），<br />\n日本酒店本身地方唔大，<br />\n除咗由布院一泊兩食，其他盡量想搵airbnb住得鬆動少少。<br />\n想知有無日本通提供一下意見，<br />\n福岡民宿住近天神村係咪較方便，又唔係好貴？"},{"pid":"efc35207dd2029994e1f1e3828678b2244f73c93","tid":1235634,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"酒店大唔大黎講... 你全部book twin room其實唔會細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f14136eec14d4171b62aff285b7331a235f6ed","tid":1235634,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"btw 如果係搭JR為主, 就住博多附近啦<br />\n搭巴士為主就住天神啦"},{"pid":"5ebac122c9b027f9bf7f9c92fde8e34721a2619b","tid":1235634,"uid":251949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62f14136eec14d4171b62aff285b7331a235f6ed","tid":1235634,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"btw 如果係搭JR為主, 就住博多附近啦<br />\n搭巴士為主就住天神啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"自駕應該就無乜大分別？"},{"pid":"10eea0ec2609aa4dd4c66955992dd95ea462da5a","tid":1235634,"uid":251949,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"efc35207dd2029994e1f1e3828678b2244f73c93","tid":1235634,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"酒店大唔大黎講... 你全部book twin room其實唔會細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:47:35.000Z","msg":"計埋成本好似BNB平少少"},{"pid":"b7e562a561a76fb25ff9fd0ce110e18d6754009d","tid":1235634,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"